title: Which of these aTokens do you MOST want to stake as Spirit Force collateral for your Aavegotchi? #VoteToList
body:
Two of these four collaterals will be selected for inclusion in the official launch of Aavegotchi, in addition to the seven already selected. 

Cast your vote using GHST to select your favorite!
 
Top TWO by total score (Twitter+Snapshot) will be listed!

The Snapshot block is roughly 7 days from the start date (Ethereum Mainnet block 11521684), so you'll need to hold GHST to vote before that happens!
author: 0x027Ffd3c119567e85998f4E6B9c3d83D5702660c
